@@TJvScreenResolution
Description:
This is the easiest way to change the resolutions of the screen and to list all resolutions supported.

================================================================
@@TJvScreenResolution.GetSupportedModes@array of TDevMode@Integer
Description:
This method list the supported resolutions. 

Parameters:
Modes - This array will contain the supported modes 
Count - This variable will countain the number of modes stored in the array

================================================================
@@TJvScreenResolution.SetMode@TDevMode
Description:
This method is for changing the resolution. 

Parameters:
Value - This is a TDevMode retrieved with the methos GetSuppotedModes.

